# Polymarket India — Cursor rules
Follow `AGENTS.md` as the source of truth.

- App Router: `src/app/`
- API routes: `src/app/api/**/route.ts`
- Skill router: `CODEX.md`
- Skills live in `.agents/skills/` (mirrors your Claude harness).
- Server-only Supabase client: `src/lib/db.ts` (never import into `"use client"` code)
- Before PRs: `npm run lint` then `npm test`
